version_description:
1. Support setting Mailmaster as the default mailbox client (please upgrade the iOS system version to 14 or higher);
2. It supports the timed sending of NetEase mailbox, and you can set a specified time to send when writing a letter;
3. Supports creating and editing contacts, and also supports directly saving and editing recipients when writing a letter;
4. When writing a letter, long press the recipient and drag to adjust the recipient's position;
5. Optimize some error prompts；
6. Finally, we have further optimized the display adaptation of reading letters to make mail reading more comfortable;

NetEase Mail Master and NetEase Mail web version, the security collaboration capabilities of both parties have been improved again:
1. It supports scanning to log in to the web version, and it is safer to log in without a password on a public computer;
2. Support to modify the password and modify the secure mobile phone binding in the app;
3. Further strengthen the security verification of adding NetEase mailbox;
4. Further strengthen the security management and synchronization capabilities of the master account;
Other updates:
1. Optimize the registration process of NetEase mailbox;
2. Search support to search emails by contact;
3. The search supports entering spaces to realize multi-keyword search;
4. Optimized the display of avatars for multi-person conversations on the mailing list
5. Optimized the copywriting of some error prompts;
6. Optimized reading and loading performance;

