The [File] is newly launched to solve a series of common problems such as large attachment sending, attachment search, attachment download management, etc.:
1. Support uploading and sending large attachments when writing a letter. Break the attachment size limit, making sending large attachments more secure;
2. The function of recent attachments can quickly find the content of recently viewed attachments, and the efficiency is further improved;
3. Local download attachment management, support to view all downloaded attachments of the current device;
4. Support cloud attachment download management, you can check the download progress and manage the download status;
5. Support local attachment cleaning, you can choose "Clean Cache" to clean up unnecessary history cache;
6. When you receive an email with cloud attachments, if it is not convenient to download at the moment, you can also choose to save it as a cloud attachment to avoid the attachment's expiration;

